msgctxt "56_Police Scanner"
msgid "This is KPD dispatch. Homicide reported in front of the Mach Bowl bowling alley, near Theater Square. "
msgstr "Este es el despacho del DPK, homicidio reportado frente al boliche de Mach Bowl, cerca de la Plaza del Teatro. "

msgctxt "68_Police Scanner"
msgid "We have positive ID on victim. Koichi Yabe, a writer residing in Kamurocho. All officers in the area respond immediately. "
msgstr "Tenemos una identificación positiva sobre la víctima. Koichi Yabe, un escritor residente en Kamurocho. Todos los oficiales de la zona reportense inmediatamente. "

msgctxt "80_Tanimura"
msgid "(A murder...)"
msgstr "(Un asesinato...)"

msgctxt "128_Tanimura"
msgid "Tanimura here."
msgstr "Aquí Tanimura."

msgctxt "140_Officer"
msgid "You listening to your radio? Get your ass over here, now. "
msgstr "¿Estás escuchando tu radio? ven aquí, ahora. "

msgctxt "152_Tanimura"
msgid "I don't get it. Why're you calling me about this? "
msgstr "No lo entiendo. ¿Por qué me llamas por esto? "

msgctxt "164_Officer"
msgid "I didn't say for you to ask questions. Just get over here NOW. "
msgstr "No te dije que hicieras preguntas. Solo ven aquí AHORA. "

msgctxt "176_Tanimura"
msgid "Yeah, yeah. Be right there. "
msgstr "Sí, sí. Ahora voy. "

msgctxt "236_Tanimura"
msgid "(What the hell? Oh well. Guess I'll head over to Mach Bowl.) "
msgstr "(¿Qué carajo? Bueno. Supongo que pasaré por Mach Bowl). "

msgctxt "248_Tanimura"
msgid "(A murder... They said the victim was a writer. Maybe I should check it out.) "
msgstr "(Un asesinato... Dijeron que la víctima era un escritor. Quizás debería echarle un vistazo.) "

msgctxt "260_Tanimura"
msgid "(I'd rather stay under the radar right now, but maybe I should check out the crime scene.) "
msgstr "(Preferiría permanecer un perfil bajo en este momento, pero tal vez debería revisar la escena del crimen.) "

msgctxt "272_Tanimura"
msgid "(The crime scene's over at Mach Bowl. I've gotta be careful.) "
msgstr "(La escena del crimen está en Mach Bowl. Debo tener cuidado.) "

